武汉第三医院光谷园区临时ICU关闭，上海重症医生团队24小时床边守护换来高治愈率。
Wuhan Third Hospital Guanggu Park temporary closure of the ICU, the Shanghai intensive care team 24 hours bedside guards in exchange for high cure rates.
黄祺。
Wangqi.
